cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AR, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper discusses convolution neural networks which are widely used in computer vision applications. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for optimizing the inference of single-image convolution neural networks, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
3. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper discusses neural networks and proposes a new algorithm for optimizing their inference. 
4. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) - The paper focuses on optimizing the convolution algorithm for mobile GPUs, which falls under the domain of hardware architecture. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for optimizing the inference of convolution neural networks on mobile GPUs, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
